@@TJvFontCombobox
<GROUP TJvFontCombobox>
Summary
  Combo box that enables the user to select a font from a drop-down list.
Description
  TJvFontCombobox is a TJvComboBox descendant which enables the user to select a
  font from a drop-down list of the face names for all fonts supported by the
  screen /installed on the system.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFontCombobox.ChangeFonts
Summary
  Initializes the fonts listed in the Fonts property.
Description
  Call ChangeFonts to initialize the list of fonts in the Fonts property using
  information held in the system.
Parameters
  Sender - Reference to the TJvFontCombobox component generating the event.
          This can be either the internal button or Self.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFontCombobox.DrawIt
Summary
  Draws the FontComboBox list component when the combobox drops open or is
  browsed.
Description
  Use this method to draw the FontComboBox list component when the combobox
  drops open or is browsed.  The method iterates through the list of Font names
  in the Fonts property and the Font name is displayed in the list using the
  corresponding Font.
Parameters
  Control - The TJvFontCombobox which is associated with this event.
  Index - The position in the list of Fonts for the displayed Font Name.
  Rect - The dimensions of the area to be drawn.
  State - The state of the associated TJvFontCombobox which must include
          the states odFocused and odSelected.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFontCombobox.Items
Summary
  The list of Font names in the list portion of the Font combo box.
Description
  Contains the list of Font names which is displayed in the drop down list of
  the FontComboBox.
  Use the FontComboBox's method of ChangeFonts to fill the list by using the
  fonts available on the system.
  Use the methods of Items to add, insert, delete and move items.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFontCombobox.Loaded
Summary
  Re-initializes the list of fonts in the Fonts property using information held
  in the system.
Description
  This method calls the ChangeFonts method. Re-initializes the list of fonts in
  the Fonts property using information held in the system.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

